hopobject.body: A law firm get prescription viagra uk The first step is getting inspectors safely into the country. The Organization for the Prohibition of Chemical Weapons has a corps of experts who have helped eliminate weapons in 15 nations and conducted inspections in 86 states. But none were in the midst of a civil war. No-fire zones around weapons depots will have to be negotiated with the Syrian government and rebel forces. This could take weeks.
